<p><span class="anchor" id="p55"></span>وَقطع بِهِ بَعضهم<a href="#p55" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p56"></span>وَتجب من قوت بَلَده<a href="#p56" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p57"></span>أى الْمخْرج وان تقوت هُوَ بِغَيْرِهِ<a href="#p57" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
